text: Quirine Oosterveld (born March 5, 1990 in Almere) is a Dutch female volleyball player. Oosterveld plays for Rote Raben Vilsbiburg and played for Alterno Apeldoorn. She has been a member of the Netherlands women's national volleyball team since 2013.
